title: Clancy's Vegetarian Emporium
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Western, Fusion, Take-out only
description: Market stall under the clock at the Cardiff Market, operating since Jan 2013. It offers some Indian as well western food to take away plus some cooking supplies to take home. No seating. The market can be accessed from St Mary Street and from the other side near St John's Church and gardens.
